highlights.text: TENBLANK has the most spots on Viral Songs Hong Kong. “旋律と結晶” is the highest at #22.
“零距离的思念” by TINY 7 has been on Viral Songs Hong Kong the longest, at 158 days straight.
“Sacred Play Secret Place” by matryoshka is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Hong Kong at #93.
“Flaming Thunder God (from "Demon Slayer: Infinity Castle") - Cover” by Diego Mitre is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Hong Kong, up 35 spots at #43.
